        "question": "定义域为 $\\mathbb{R}$ 的函数 $f(x)$ 满足：当 $x\\in [0,1)$ 时，$f(x) = 2^{x} - x$，且对任意实数 $x$，均有 $f(x) + f(x + 1) = 1$。记 $a = \\log_{2}3$，则表达式 $f(a) + f(2a) + f(3a)$ 的值为______。",
        "solution": [
            "根据条件可知，当 $n$ 为奇数时，$f(x + n) = 1 - f(x)$；当 $n$ 为偶数时，$f(x + n) = f(x)$",
            "注意到 $a = \\log_{2}3 \\in [1, 2)$，$2a = \\log_{2}9 \\in [3, 4)$，$3a = \\log_{2}27 \\in [4, 5)$",
            "所以",
            "$f(a) + f(2a) + f(3a) = 1 - f(a - 1) + 1 - f(2a - 3) + f(3a - 4)$",
            "$= 2 - f(\\log_{2}\\frac{3}{2}) - f(\\log_{2}\\frac{9}{8}) + f(\\log_{2}\\frac{27}{16})$",
            "$= 2 - (\\frac{3}{2} - \\log_{2}\\frac{3}{2}) - (\\frac{9}{8} - \\log_{2}\\frac{9}{8}) + (\\frac{27}{16} - \\log_{2}\\frac{27}{16})$",
            "$= \\frac{17}{16} + (\\log_{2}\\frac{3}{2} + \\log_{2}\\frac{9}{8} - \\log_{2}\\frac{27}{16}) = \\frac{17}{16}$"
        ],
        "final_answer": ["$\\frac{17}{16}$"],
        "is_multiple_answer": false,
        "unit": null,
        "answer_type": "Expression",
        "error": null
    },
