        "context": "2021年全国高中数学联合竞赛A2卷解答题",
        "question": "已知 $\\triangle ABC$ 满足 $AB = 1$，$AC = 2$，$\\cos B + \\sin C = 1$，求 $BC$ 边的长。",
        "solution": [
            "记 $a = BC, b = AC, c = AB$，于是 $b = 2, c = 1$",
            "由正弦定理知 $\\frac{\\sin B}{\\sin C} = \\frac{b}{c} = 2$，即 $\\sin B = 2\\sin C$",
            "又 $\\cos B = 1 - \\sin C$，所以 $(2\\sin C)^{2} + (1 - \\sin C)^{2} = \\sin^{2}B + \\cos^{2}B = 1$",
            "化简得 $5\\sin^{2}C - 2\\sin C = 0$。又 $\\sin C \\neq 0$，故 $\\sin C = \\frac{2}{5}$",
            "进而 $\\cos B = 1 - \\sin C = \\frac{3}{5}$",
            "由余弦定理得 $\\cos B = \\frac{a^{2} + c^{2} - b^{2}}{2ac}$，于是 $\\frac{3}{5} = \\frac{a^{2} - 3}{2a}$，即 $a^{2} - \\frac{6}{5}a - 3 = 0$",
            "又 $a > 0$，解得 $a = \\frac{3 + 2\\sqrt{21}}{5}$",
            "即 $BC$ 边的长为 $\\frac{3 + 2\\sqrt{21}}{5}$"
        ],
        "final_answer": ["$\\frac{3 + 2\\sqrt{21}}{5}$"],
        "is_multiple_answer": false,
        "unit": null,
        "answer_type": "Expression",
        "error": null
    },
