        "id": 20210126,
        "subfield": "Function",
        "context": "2021年全国高中数学联合竞赛A2卷解答题",
        "question": "设 $a, b$ 为实数，函数 $f(x) = x^{3} + ax^{2} + bx$。若存在三个实数 $x_{1}, x_{2}, x_{3}$ 满足 $x_{1} + 1 \\leq x_{2} \\leq x_{3} - 1$，且 $f(x_{1}) = f(x_{2}) = f(x_{3})$，求 $|a| + 2|b|$ 的最小值。",
        "solution": [
            "对满足条件的函数 $f(x)$ 及实数 $x_{1}, x_{2}, x_{3}$，设 $f(x_{1}) = f(x_{2}) = f(x_{3}) = c$，则 $x_{1}, x_{2}, x_{3}$ 为三次方程 $x^{3} + ax^{2} + bx - c = 0$ 的三个实根",
            "由韦达定理知 $a = -(x_{1} + x_{2} + x_{3}), b = x_{1}x_{2} + x_{2}x_{3} + x_{3}x_{1}$",
            "又由条件知 $x_{2} - x_{1} \\geq 1, x_{3} - x_{2} \\geq 1, x_{3} - x_{1} \\geq 2$",
            "故 $a^{2} - 3b = x_{1}^{2} + x_{2}^{2} + x_{3}^{2} - x_{1}x_{2} - x_{2}x_{3} - x_{3}x_{1}$",
            "$= \\frac{1}{2}((x_{1} - x_{2})^{2} + (x_{2} - x_{3})^{2} + (x_{3} - x_{1})^{2}) \\geq \\frac{1}{2}(1 + 1 + 4) = 3$",
            "即 $b \\leq \\frac{a^{2}}{3} - 1$",
            "若 $|a| \\geq \\sqrt{3}$，则 $|a| + 2|b| \\geq |a| \\geq \\sqrt{3}$",
            "若 $0 \\leq |a| < \\sqrt{3}$，则 $b \\leq \\frac{a^{2}}{3} - 1 < 0$，注意到此时 $|a| - \\frac{3}{4} < \\sqrt{3} - \\frac{3}{4}$",
            "所以 $|a| + 2|b| \\geq |a| + \\frac{2}{3}(3 - a^{2}) = -\\frac{2}{3}(|a| - \\frac{3}{4})^{2} + \\frac{19}{8}$",
            "$> -\\frac{2}{3}(\\sqrt{3} - \\frac{3}{4})^{2} + \\frac{19}{8} = \\sqrt{3}$",
            "以上表明 $|a| + 2|b| \\geq \\sqrt{3}$",
            "另一方面，当 $a = \\sqrt{3}, b = 0$ 时，实数 $x_{1} = -1 - \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{3}, x_{2} = -\\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{3}, x_{3} = 1 - \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{3}$ 满足条件（$f(x_{1}), f(x_{2}), f(x_{3})$ 的值均为 $\\frac{2\\sqrt{3}}{9}$），此时 $|a| + 2|b| = \\sqrt{3}$",
            "综上所述，$|a| + 2|b|$ 的最小值为 $\\sqrt{3}$"
        ],
        "final_answer": ["$\\sqrt{3}$"],
        "is_multiple_answer": false,
        "unit": null,
        "answer_type": "Expression",
        "error": null
    },
